features: Upper: A high impact, sporty sandal for all-day wear. Full grain leather in forefoot and medial/lateral instep straps. Air mesh textile strap with reflective webbing detail in center instep. Hook and loop closure. Synthetic lining
Midsole: A unique modular design that feels comfortably light underfoot. EVA midsole with TPU heel logo
Outsole: Molded rubber outsole with oversized signature Sorel scallops
